Title: Monitoring of Fortinet FortiMail Servers
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1613987157
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

This werk introduces new check plugins which monitor Fortinet FortiMail
servers:
<ul>
<li><tt>fortimail_cpu_load</tt>: Monitors the CPU load.</li>
<li><tt>fortimail_disk_usage</tt>: Monitors the disk usage.</li>
<li><tt>fortimail_queue</tt>: Monitors mail queue lengths.</li>
</ul>
Furthermore, the new inventory plugin <tt>fortimail_system</tt> inventorizes
the model and the serial number as well as the OS version of the server.
